{"tid":1356991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"與其大嗌林鄭下台 不如高呼回應訴求","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:06:50.000Z","uid":44754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc73eb9c77b0c3dc7cdd5c131f9839fbcde5fb4","tid":1356991,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"大家都知道五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n#撤回逃犯條例<br />\n#撤回暴動定性<br />\n#撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n#追究警隊濫暴<br />\n#立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n但總係有人行街時無啦啦大嗌林鄭下台/落地獄<br />\n既然大家咁掛住林鄭<br />\n倒不如嗌完五大訴求之後<br />\n口號緊接嗌<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥 回應訴求!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n盡量將活動焦點放返喺政府身上<br />\n逼佢無得回避<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人嘅訴求</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f583ced737ba52562d4ccd8530da97a653b041a5","tid":1356991,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56d84345a56162af890e5fcf26bdb17df6a38cb3","tid":1356991,"uid":237077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1bb0f7bdfcb0a45bb268f0009c40528191f6087","tid":1356991,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd817adc92be2fc42c7a813898c1aabc1b69a103","tid":1356991,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"603f883359473e92887eed8d403b459271f57c17","tid":1356991,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f83554d81d6b7af47ac3e23eaefc9d0a8ed5d50","tid":1356991,"uid":44754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"推俾多啲人見到"},{"pid":"ab2ffd9